Email: Please click here

If any items lost on airport grounds or on the flight to Salzburg are passed to the Salzburg Airport Services SAS and taken to the lost property office of the city of Salzburg (Schloss Mirabell) after six weeks.

Please contact Lost property in Mirabell Palace, Mirabellplatz 4, ground floor, entrance 3.
Opening times: Monday to Thursday 7:30 a.m. to 4:00 p.m., Friday 7:30 a.m. to 1:00 p.m.

For electronic lost property service to search for lost items, please click Online search

First aid Service at Mozart Salzburg Airport (Salzburg Airport W.A. Mozart)

First aid station Opening times: Daily from 5:30 a.m. to 11:00 p.m.
Ambulance service location: 1st floor of the main terminal, entrance A (bulky luggage)

Parking

Email: info@salzburg-airport.at
Opening times: Daily from 8:00 a.m. to 6:30 p.m.
